fields.name: Masamune nodachi
fields.description:
The Nodachi razor has a longer handle and an amplified blade feeling. All in favour of a closer and sharper shaving experience.

Nodachi is for more experienced users who like a more efficient shave. It’s usually used by people with a more irregular and stronger beard.

The closed comb plate is our smoothest option and the most popular. It is designed with small grooves along the edges of the plate giving less blade exposure to the skin.

fields.name: Muramasa Adjustable Razor
fields.description:
The Muramasa is a highly efficient and comfortable adjustable safety razor that allows shavers to choose the preferred shave setting (smooth or aggressive) by simply turning the razor dial.

Due to its fine-tuning adjustable mechanism and superior construction quality, it provides an adaptable shave. Perfect for both wet shaving beginners and experts.

The Muramasa adapts to your skin and hair but it’s also perfect for a rushed shave if you need a more forgiving setting, or if your mood simply demands something new.

fields.name: ARENA Smoked
fields.description:
A full inch blade, dark as night, engraved with a proud lion, requires courage to wield it in the face. 

This courage is what the blade represents. It was inspired by Theodore Roosevelt's speech entitled "Citizenship in a Republic". An excerpt from this speech, known as "The Man in the Arena" , is engraved in full on the back of this special blade.

The speech says that it is not the critic who counts, but that all the credit goes to the man in the arena who dares a lot.

fields.name: BISMARCK EBENHOLZ
fields.description: The DOVO razor No. 2 in 6/8 inch is called BISMARCK®. In the 20th century, as it still is today, the name stands for the highest razor art from Solingen. The special features of this model are its characteristic, elegant appearance, its heavy weight and its incomparable handling.

fields.name: PRIMO II safety razor
fields.description:
The PRIMO II: Decades of experience condensed into a shaving masterpiece.

The name PRIMO means "at the beginning". PRIMO stands for a new beginning. A new beginning for you, the wet razor. More than a century of knowledge, condensed in 2 years of development time, with a painful number of development cycles, has produced this incomparable shaving tool. Made in GERMANY, of course.

When wet shaving, a tiny difference in the geometry of the razor has a fundamental impact on your shaving experience. Our goal was to create the most intense and satisfying shaving experience possible. And, to the chagrin of all other safety razors, we succeeded.

Happy is the person who makes PRIMO a permanent part of their skincare routine. A meditative state that is unparalleled.

fields.name: Proof Whiskey Razor
fields.description:
Crafted in Montana, the Proof Single Blade stands as a testament to American craftsmanship. This tool is not just a razor; it's an embodiment of durability and comfort.

Designed with an innovative pivoting head, it adapts seamlessly to the contours of your face, ensuring a close and comfortable shave. Our unique single-blade design glides smoothly across your skin, eliminating irritation and ingrown hairs.

Engineered with a magnet-secured cap, blade changes are simple and secure. The flow-through razor head design prevents clogging, ensuring a clean shave every time.

Made from CNC machined aluminum, the Proof Single Blade is built to last a lifetime, destined to become an integral and cherished part of your grooming routine.

Each razor comes encased in a genuine leather case, stitched together in Montana, chosen for its enduring quality and unparalleled durability, ensuring it lasts as long as the razor itself.

fields.name: Leaf Razor
fields.description:
The unique and patent-protected Leaf Razor is the first safety razor designed to address the needs of body shavers and head shavers.
A pivoting head, Adjustable closeness, Triple-blade shave, Magnetic loading assist, Zero disposable plastic
There are other metal razors, but there are no other Leaf Razors. We welcome you to try us as the best way to experience the difference.

fields.name: Twig
fields.description: Leaf single-edge razors, Twig an. If you've used an old-school safety razor before you'll be surprised at how easy it is to pick up and shave with Leaf Twig.

fields.name: DOVO Shavette Stainless
fields.description: The DOVO Shavette is a straight razor with interchangeable blades. It can be used just like a classic straight razor. The possibility to change the blade makes it extremely popular at barbershops since every customer receives a fresh blade. This stainless steel design has a beautiful shine on the tang and back, while the handle is kept matt.

fields.name: DOVO Shavette Olive Wood
fields.description: The DOVO Shavette is a straight razor with interchangeable blades. It can be used just like a classic straight razor. fields.name: Muramasa Adjustable Brush - Synthetic
fields.description:
It’s a type of brush that allows the user to adjust the length of the bristles, also known as the loft. This allows the user to customize the firmness or softness of the bristles to suit their specific needs. For example, a softer setting may be more suitable for creating a rich lather, while a firmer setting may be better for scrubbing and cleaning the skin.

This innovative and patented Adjustable Shaving Brush, designed for easy loft adjustment during shaving and compatible with various hair types, is suitable for all skin and hair types. It offers a personalized shaving experience, unlocking the full potential of different brush hair types.

Synthetic: Excellent lather and is easy to maintain. It dries quickly and doesn’t require the same conditioning as natural hair brushes.

Loft: [48 – 58] mm
Ø Knot: 24 mm
Handle height: 51 mm
Weight: 114 grams

fields.name: Masamune Brush Synthetic
fields.description:
The Synthetic Shaving Brush offers excellent lathering and exfoliating properties for a comfortable shave. It is also easy to maintain, as it dries quickly and does not require conditioning as natural hair brushes do.

We refused to settle for the standard synthetic hairs available in the market. Instead, our dedicated efforts have led us to develop a brush that exemplifies a unique balance between backbone and softness with optimal fiber density, resulting in exceptional lathering capability and remarkable water retention.

The handle is CNC machined in AISI 303 high-grade stainless steel, hand-finished, and sandblasted.

Knot Height: 50 mm

fields.name: Proraso Sensitive Shaving Soap
fields.description:
This formula, ideal for sensitive skin, provides a creamy lather for a close shave without razor burn or irritation. Oatmeal and green tea calm, soothe, and protect inflamed, irritated skin.
Creates a rich, thick lather while protecting, calming, and soothing skin prone to irritation.

fields.name: Proraso  Eucalyptus
fields.description:
This Proraso classic provides a dense, creamy lather to prepare skin for a close shave without nicks and cuts. Eucalyptus purifies and tones while menthol adds a refreshing, cooling sensation.
Benefits
Creates a rich, thick lather and softens skin for a close shave without nicks and cuts
Suggested Use
Apply with a shave brush to damp skin; work up a rich lather. Use after applying Proraso Pre-Shave Cream.

fields.name: Cella Organic Aloe Vera Shaving Soap
fields.description: Naturally practical! The organic shaving cream in the tube from Cella ensures a precise and comfortable shave with valuable organic oils and natural ingredients. The shaving cream in the tube has been specially developed to lather directly on the face and quickly transforms into a rich and soft lather. The soft, creamy lather allows a comfortable shave and protects the skin from irritation and micro-cuts. At the same time, the shaving cream moisturizes and leaves the skin feeling pleasantly soft.dambiro

fields.name: Tabac shaving soap
fields.description: Launched by the design house of Maurer & Wirtz in 1959. It possesses a blend of lavender, citrus, and warm florals. It is recommended for casual wear.

fields.name: Beau Brummell
fields.description:
SOLID BLACK MARBLE: Handcrafted from a solid block of natural black marble stone. Features horizontally cut grooves on the bowls interior to help better whip shaving cream or soap into a dense lather.
NATURALLY HEAT RETAINING: Run your shaving bowl under hot water for 1 minute to heat up the natural stone. Bowl will naturally retain the heat and warm up your shaving lather for a more comfortable shave.
SIZE DONE RIGHT: Bowl is just the right size, It is large enough to use any shaving brush to easily work up a rich, thick, luxurious lather yet small enough to fit comfortably in your hand. 4.5-inch diameter, 2.5-inch height, 0.27-inch wall thickness, 2.5-inch base diameter, 1.3-pound weight.
BEST QUALITY: A truly high-quality bowl, made of a solid block of heavy black marble Crafted of black marble, this shaving bowl is as much about the look as it is about utility.
BEAU BRUMMELL FOR MEN creates expertly formulated men’s skincare and grooming products. We pride ourselves on the quality and ingredients of our moisturizer to ensure our customers receive the best we have to offer and real benefits for all skin types. Featured in GQ, Glamour, Men's Journal, Primer Magazine, and more.

fields.name: Grandslam Wooden Shaving Bowl
fields.description:
he Oak wood bowl is just the right size, easily work up a rich, thick, luxurious lather to complete shave with a normal sized brush.
Perfect lid to prevent dust, keep clean and dry.
BUILDS RICH FOAM : Used with shaving soap , shaving brush together with hot water to whip up a rich, creamy lather for wet shaving.
This wooden bowl and lid have a genuine wood grain and luster that may well make them the most beautiful thing in your bathroom—beside your clean-shaven face, of course.
NATURALLY DURABLE: Oak wood is solid, edge-security without hurting hands.it is also a perfect size for travelling as well.
